## Allowlist Mode Rule
- This workspace may run with `tools.exec.security=allowlist`.
- Do not use shell line continuations (`\` + newline), heredocs, or multi-line shell commands for API calls.
- Prefer single-line commands only.
- Keep `curl` invocations on one line.
- If you need formatting, do it in markdown output, not in the shell command.

